{"timestamp":"2026-06-09T08:39:00.343Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"Progress made:\n\n- Finished `#67` minimal Playwright fixes and pushed the rebased stack from `#67` upward.\n- Fixed `#69` review feedback in two focused batches:\n  - Restored QR registration authorization.\n  - Fixed transfer redemption for public options, required-question options, gross transfer pricing, and pending-transfer uniqueness in migration SQL.\n  - Applied mechanical quick wins: runtime env JSON parse narrowing, duotone edit icon, stable user-list spec path, `type=\"button\"` on event edit menu, tenant-scoped account-doc cleanup.\n- Resolved the review threads covered by those changes.\n- Rebased and pushed `#70`, `#71`, and `codex/stabilization-flow-coverage` after each `#69` amendment.\n- Validation passed locally: `bun run lint`, `bun run format:write`, targeted Vitest checks, and `bun run build:app`.\n\nCurrent state:\n- `#69` has no failing checks detected, but CI is still rerunning.\n- `#69` still has 15 unresolved review threads, mostly the remaining server/test robustness comments. I left those open rather than mixing heavier concurrency/email fixes into the same patch.\n- Worktree is clean on `codex/pr62-split-09-finance-docs-captions`.\n\n::git-stage{cwd=\"/Users/hedde/code/evorto\"}\n::git-commit{cwd=\"/Users/hedde/code/evorto\"}\n::git-push{cwd=\"/Users/hedde/code/evorto\" branch=\"codex/pr62-split-05-role-doc-flow\"}\n::git-push{cwd=\"/Users/hedde/code/evorto\" branch=\"codex/pr62-split-06-browser-transport-blocker\"}\n::git-push{cwd=\"/Users/hedde/code/evorto\" branch=\"codex/pr62-split-07-organizer-receipt-query\"}\n::git-push{cwd=\"/Users/hedde/code/evorto\" branch=\"codex/pr62-split-08-active-head-ci-cleanup\"}\n::git-push{cwd=\"/Users/hedde/code/evorto\" branch=\"codex/pr62-split-09-finance-docs-captions\"}\n::git-push{cwd=\"/Users/hedde/code/evorto\" branch=\"codex/stabilization-flow-coverage\"}\n\n","phase":"final_answer","memory_